Class OneLine

java.lang.Object
  OneLine
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<OneLine>
public class OneLine
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<OneLine>

Record class that is used in a DLL. creates a string for a name, office, courses teaching as well as a phone number for each record's instance. Accessor and mutator methods for these attributes and a compareTo to compare records and a readRecord in order to read the actual records. Includes a toString method in order to convert all attributes into a string and formatting into one record.

Version:
1.00 2011-01-11
Author:
Duncan A. Buell modifications by Leonardo Merza
